{"tid":1139026,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"羅致光：沒有貧富懸殊現象便沒有今天的我","createTime":"2019-05-05T02:59:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-05T06:03:16.000Z","uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"5dc08f790c409e0017f48f39f82978f9f83bc8b2","tid":1139026,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T02:59:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190505/s00001/3a1e9c37dac14195b818cabadb22154c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190505%2Fs00001%2F3a1e9c37dac14195b818cabadb22154c.jpg&h=1d3fdd71&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n勞工及福利局長羅致光發表網誌談及貧富懸殊，形容「沒有貧富懸殊現象，便沒有今天的我」。<br />\n<br />\n網誌題為＜貧富懸殊的挑戰＞，羅致光指出，貧富懸殊現象不是新鮮事物，只是愈演愈烈，並憶述自己投身社工緣由，「四十一年前的一天，我還是銀行的一名電腦程序編寫員，在電腦房中看着銀行的交易總額以每秒過百萬跳升時，計一計自己工作的邊際貢獻，和自己薪酬一比，自己所得的不及十分一，但同時又覺得自己薪酬遠較一般工人為高時，便決定投身社工行業」。<br />\n<br />\n羅致光又說，從過往數年香港貧窮情況分析，就業對脫貧及減低收入不均重要，政府制定適時政策責無旁貸，惟亦需要凝聚社會共識，政策制定與推行才能順暢。<br />\n<br />\n羅致光另提及2016年香港堅尼系數，稱「只是反映收入不均的程度（income gap），並非是財富不均 （wealth gap）」。堅尼系數旨在反映社會貧富差距情況，2016年香港稅前福利轉移前堅尼系數為0.539，屬45年來新高，稅後福利轉移後則降至0.473。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190505/s00001/1557023144095/%E7%BE%85%E8%87%B4%E5%85%89-%E6%B2%92%E6%9C%89%E8%B2%A7%E5%AF%8C%E6%87%B8%E6%AE%8A%E7%8F%BE%E8%B1%A1%E4%BE%BF%E6%B2%92%E6%9C%89%E4%BB%8A%E5%A4%A9%E7%9A%84%E6%88%91\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190505%2Fs00001%2F1557023144095%2F%25E7%25BE%2585%25E8%2587%25B4%25E5%2585%2589-%25E6%25B2%2592%25E6%259C%2589%25E8%25B2%25A7%25E5%25AF%258C%25E6%2587%25B8%25E6%25AE%258A%25E7%258F%25BE%25E8%25B1%25A1%25E4%25BE%25BF%25E6%25B2%2592%25E6%259C%2589%25E4%25BB%258A%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E7%259A%2584%25E6%2588%2591&d=CFSJobiERGKWyjxxKHv2y%2BIUDtzVwJRUTDGgxy4aIpc%3D&h=b2874fe4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190505%2Fs00001%2F1557023144095%2F%25E7%25BE%2585%25E8%2587%25B4%25E5%2585%2589-%25E6%25B2%2592%25E6%259C%2589%25E8%25B2%25A7%25E5%25AF%258C%25E6%2587%25B8%25E6%25AE%258A%25E7%258F%25BE%25E8%25B1%25A1%25E4%25BE%25BF%25E6%25B2%2592%25E6%259C%2589%25E4%25BB%258A%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E7%259A%2584%25E6%2588%2591&h=f1e8fbd3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190505/s00001/1557023144095/%E7%BE%85%E8%87%B4%E5%85%89-%E6%B2%92%E6%9C%89%E8%B2%A7%E5%AF%8C%E6%87%B8%E6%AE%8A%E7%8F%BE%E8%B1%A1%E4%BE%BF%E6%B2%92%E6%9C%89%E4%BB%8A%E5%A4%A9%E7%9A%84%E6%88%91</a>"},{"pid":"625fb918d79aa1825d2043f406492403d52122a9","tid":1139026,"uid":249885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T03:00:36.000Z","msg":"呢條友都識it 咁勁"},{"pid":"b53754da46715013e50ea83c8c2dd4e5c1264ed0","tid":1139026,"uid":20241,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T03:02:30.000Z","msg":"想屌佢<br />\n但覺得屌來都多鳩餘"},{"pid":"ff5b5b6880dbbcd44eebfc322ec17fae47fd108d","tid":1139026,"uid":985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T03:04:20.000Z","msg":"就算政府要補貼，都唔見得會有我份。"},{"pid":"adb93ba6ecbb5e1aa790775149b77013f9235d44","tid":1139026,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ff5b5b6880dbbcd44eebfc322ec17fae47fd108d","tid":1139026,"uid":985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T03:04:20.000Z","msg":"就算政府要補貼，都唔見得會有我份。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T03:11:14.000Z","msg":"總有人要負責做貧嗰邊嘅"},{"pid":"fd7618e063ad701c0ef59b533ab03408502ee3f8","tid":1139026,"uid":35014,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T03:13:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cd8f22d8fd87b5cdb65fe62764ab2698fbf88e27","tid":1139026,"uid":5523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T03:16:40.000Z","msg":"It 之光？"},{"pid":"623e242ca6c250ef9c98952d243c0a5a13ee89ac","tid":1139026,"uid":58852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,